uest` trigger for main branch\n84:   - Purpose: Trigger on PR to main\n85:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n86:   - Verification: `grep \"pull_request:\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n87: \n88: - [ ] **T3.4**: Define `filter` job with `dorny/paths-filter@v3`\n89:   - Purpose: Detect Go file changes\n90:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n91:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n92: \n93: - [ ] **T3.5**: Add path filter for `lint: ['**/*.go', 'go.mod', 'go.sum', '.golangci.yml']`\n94:   - Purpose: Filter for Go-related changes\n95:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n96:   - Verification: `grep \"'\\\\*\\\\*/\\\\*.go'\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n97: \n98: - [ ] **T3.6**: Define `lint` job with `if: needs.filter.outputs.lint == 'true'`\n99:   - Purpose: Conditional job execution\n100:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n101:   - Verification: `grep \"needs.filter.outputs.lint\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n102: \n103: - [ ] **T3.7**: Add `actions/setup-go@v5` step with `go-version: '1.24'`\n104:   - Purpose: Install Go toolchain\n105:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n106:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: actions/setup-go@v5\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n107: \n108: - [ ] **T3.8**: Add `make lint` step\n109:   - Purpose: Run golangci-lint\n110:   - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n111:   - Verification: `grep \"make lint\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n112: \n113: ### Phase 4: test-coverage.yml - Go Coverage + Codecov (ST-4)\n114: \n115: - [ ] **T4.1**: Create workflow file `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n116:   - Purpose: Initialize coverage workflow file\n117:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n118:   - Verification: `test -f .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n119: \n120: - [ ] **T4.2**: Add workflow name \"Go Test Coverage\"\n121:   - Purpose: Define workflow display name\n122:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n123:   - Verification: `grep \"name: Go Test Coverage\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n124: \n125: - [ ] **T4.3**: Add `on: pull_request` and `on: push` triggers\n126:   - Purpose: Trigger on PR and push events\n127:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n128:   - Verification: `grep \"pull_request:\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n129: \n130: - [ ] **T4.4**: Add `workflow_call` for CODECOV_TOKEN secret\n131:   - Purpose: Enable reusable workflow with secrets\n132:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n133:   - Verification: `grep \"workflow_call:\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n134: \n135: - [ ] **T4.5**: Define `filter` job with coverage path filter\n136:   - Purpose: Detect relevant file changes\n137:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n138:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n139: \n140: - [ ] **T4.6**: Define `coverage` job with conditional execution\n141:   - Purpose: Run tests only when changes detected\n142:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n143:   - Verification: `grep \"needs.filter.outputs.coverage\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n144: \n145: - [ ] **T4.7**: Add `actions/setup-go@v5` with `go-version: '1.24'`\n146:   - Purpose: Install Go toolchain\n147:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n148:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: actions/setup-go@v5\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n149: \n150: - [ ] **T4.8**: Add `go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/...` step\n151:   - Purpose: Run tests with race detector and coverage\n152:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n153:   - Verification: `grep \"go test -race\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n154: \n155: - [ ] **T4.9**: Add `actions/upload-artifact@v4` for coverage.out\n156:   - Purpose: Store coverage artifact\n157:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n158:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n159: \n160: - [ ] **T4.10**: Add `codecov/codecov-action@v4` step\n161:   - Purpose: Upload coverage to Codecov\n162:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n163:   - Verification: `grep \"uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n164: \n165: - [ ] **T4.11**: Add `fail_ci_if_error: false` for Codecov action\n166:   - Purpose: Non-blocking coverage upload\n167:   - File: `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n168:   - Verification: `grep \"fail_ci_if_error: false\" .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n169: \n170: ### Phase 5: codegen-check.yml - Generated Code Drift (ST-5)\n171: \n172: - [ ] **T5.1**: Create workflow file `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n173:   - Purpose: Initialize codegen check workflow file\n174:   - File: `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n175:   - Verification: `test -f .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n176: \n177: - [ ] **T5.2**: Add workflow name \"Codegen Check\"\n178:   - Purpose: Define workflow display name\n179:   - File: `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n180:   - Verification: `grep \"name: Codegen Check\" .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n181: \n182: - [ ] **T5.3**: Add `on: pull_request` trigger for main branch\n183:   - Purpose: Trigger on PR to main\n184:   - File: `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n185:   - Verification: `grep \"pull_request:\" .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n186: \n187: - [ ] **T5.4**: Define `filter` job with codegen path filter\n188:   - Purpose: Detect API/hack file changes\n189:   - File: `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n190:   - Verification: `grep \"pkg/apis\" .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n191: \n192: - [ ] **T5.5**: Define `codegen` job with conditional execution\n193:   - Purpose: Run only when codegen files changed\n194:   - File: `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n195:   - Verification: `grep \"needs.filter.outputs.codegen\" .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n196: \n197: - [ ] **T5.6**: Add `actions/setup-go@v5` wi