916: \n917: ---\n918: \n919: ## Acceptance Criteria\n920: \n921: - [ ] `.github/workflows/` directory exists\n922: - [ ] 12 workflow YAML files exist in `.github/workflows/`\n923: - [ ] `main.yml` triggers on pull_request and push to main\n924: - [ ] `lint.yml` uses `dorny/paths-filter@v3` for Go file changes\n925: - [ ] `test-coverage.yml` has `workflow_call` for CODECOV_TOKEN\n926: - [ ] `test-coverage.yml` uploads to Codecov with `fail_ci_if_error: false`\n927: - [ ] `codegen-check.yml` runs `make gen-all` and `git diff --exit-code`\n928: - [ ] `copyright-check.yml` runs `make gen-copyright` and checks drift\n929: - [ ] `codespell.yml` runs spelling check with skip patterns\n930: - [ ] `python-sdk-tests.yml` runs pytest in sdk-python directory\n931: - [ ] `python-lint.yml` runs Ruff with `pyproject.toml` config\n932: - [ ] `e2e.yml` creates Kind cluster named `agentcube-e2e`\n933: - [ ] `e2e.yml` has cleanup in `if: always()` block\n934: - [ ] `e2e.yml` uploads logs on failure\n935: - [ ] `build-push-release.yml` triggers on `v*` tags\n936: - [ ] `build-push-release.yml` builds multi-arch (linux/amd64, linux/arm64)\n937: - [ ] `build-push-release.yml` pushes to ghcr.io\n938: - [ ] `dify-plugin-publish.yml` triggers on `dify-plugin/v*` tags\n939: - [ ] `dify-plugin-publish.yml` creates PR to `langgenius/dify-plugins`\n940: - [ ] `workflows-approve.yml` uses `pull_request_target` for secrets access\n941: - [ ] `workflows-approve.yml` checks `ok-to-test` label\n942: - [ ] `filters.yaml` defines all 6 filter categories (lint, sdk, python, coverage, codegen, copyright)\n943: - [ ] All workflows use consistent action versions (checkout@v4, setup-go@v5, setup-python@v5)\n944: - [ ] All workflow files have valid YAML syntax\n945: - [ ] All workflow filenames follow lowercase-hyphen naming convention\n946: \n947: ---\n948: \n949: ## File Changes Summary\n950: \n951: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n952: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n953: | `.github/` | Create | - | GitHub configuration directory |\n954: | `.github/workflows/` | Create | - | Workflows directory |\n955: | `.github/workflows/main.yml` | Create | ~30 | PR Docker build verification |\n956: | `.github/workflows/lint.yml` | Create | ~50 | Go lint with path filter |\n957: | `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` | Create | ~60 | Go coverage + Codecov |\n958: | `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` | Create | ~50 | Generated code drift check |\n959: | `.github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` | Create | ~50 | Copyright header check |\n960: | `.github/workflows/codespell.yml` | Create | ~80 | Spelling verification |\n961: | `.github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` | Create | ~40 | Python SDK pytest |\n962: | `.github/workflows/python-lint.yml` | Create | ~50 | Python Ruff lint |\n963: | `.github/workflows/e2e.yml` | Create | ~80 | E2E tests on Kind |\n964: | `.github/workflows/build-push-release.yml` | Create | ~100 | Multi-arch image push |\n965: | `.github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Create | ~120 | Dify plugin release |\n966: | `.github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml` | Create | ~70 | Auto-approve trusted |\n967: | `.github/workflows/filters.yaml` | Create | ~20 | Centralized path filters |\n968: \n969: **Total: 14 new files, ~780 lines**\n970: \n971: ---\n972: \n973: ## Implementation Notes\n974: \n975: ### Workflow Structure Template\n976: \n977: ```yaml\n978: name: \"<Workflow Name>\"\n979: on:\n980:   pull_request:\n981:     branches:\n982:       - main\n983:       - 'release-*'\n984: \n985: jobs:\n986:   filter:\n987:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n988:     outputs:\n989:       changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.<filter-name> }}\n990:     steps:\n991:       - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n992:       - uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3\n993:         with:\n994:           filters: .github/workflows/filters.yaml\n995: \n996:   <job-name>:\n997:     needs: filter\n998:     if: needs.filter.outputs.changed == 'true'\n999:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n1000:     steps:\n1001:       - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n1002:       - <action-specific-steps>\n1003: ```\n1004: \n1005: ### E2E Failure Handler Pattern\n1006: \n1007: ```yaml\n1008: - name: Upload E2E logs on failure\n1009:   if: failure()\n1010:   uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4\n1011:   with:\n1012:     name: e2e-logs\n1013:     path: e2e-logs/\n1014:     retention-days: 7\n1015: \n1016: - name: Cleanup E2E resources\n1017:   if: always()\n1018:   run: make e2e-clean\n1019:   continue-on-error: true\n1020: ```\n1021: \n1022: ### Multi-Arch Docker Build Pattern\n1023: \n1024: ```yaml\n1025: - name: Build and push multi-arch\n1026:   uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n1027: - uses: docker/login-action@v3\n1028:   with:\n1029:     registry: ghcr.io\n1030:     username: ${{ github.actor }}\n1031:     password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n1032: - run: |\n1033:     docker buildx build \\\n1034:       --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n1035:       --push \\\n1036:       -t ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}/workloadmanager:${{ env.TAG }} \\\n1037:       -f docker/Dockerfile .\n1038: ```\n1039: \n1040: ---\n1041: \n1042: ## Implementation Timeline\n1043: \n1044: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n1045: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n1046: | Phase 1: Directory Setup | T1.1-T1.2 | Pending | 0% |\n1047: | Phase 2: main.yml | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1048: | Phase 3: lint.yml | T3.1-T3.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1049: | Phase 4: test-coverage.yml | T4.1-T4.11 | Pending | 0% |\n1050: | Phase 5: codegen-check.yml | T5.1-T5.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1051: | Phase 6: copyright-check.yml | T6.1-T6.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1052: | Phase 7: codespell.yml | T7.1-T7.7 | Pending | 0% |\n1053: | Phase 8: python-sdk-tests.yml | T8.1-T8.9 | Pending | 0% |\n1054: | Phase 9: python-lint.yml | T9.1-T9.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1055: | Phase 10: e2e.yml | T10.1-T10.19 | Pending | 0% |\n1056: | Phase 11: build-push-release.yml | T11.1-T11.10 | Pending | 0% |\n1057: | Phase 12: dify-plugin-publ